aks to make your studying more effective.\r\n5. Find an accountability partner to keep you on track.\r\n6. Take care of your health to perform at your best during exams.\r\n7. Utilize UCT's study spaces for a focused environment.\r\n\r\nBy following these steps, you'll be well-prepared for exam season, and you'll have a better chance of doing well.",
